            "answer_text": "Ragnarok is the \u201cTwilight of the Gods.\u201d It\u2019s basically the end of the god\u2019s reign on Earth. All the gods lose their lives. Thor gives his to Jormungard to destroy him, Odin is devoured by Fenrir, Loki and Heimdall slay each other, Mani and Solveig are devoured by Hati and Skoll, Frey battles Surtur, Tyr and Garm slay each other. Odin is avenged by his son Vidar. Balder emerges from the underworld with his brother Hoder. Odin\u2019s son, Vali also survives as does Thor\u2019s sons Magni and Modi. They traveled to Idavoll and built a temple to Gimle, which was basically the Norse name for God or Jesus, meaning Christianity had reached the German and Norse lands. ",
